  "detailed_description": "PIP 2 — cute puzzle game with pipes. Your goal is to connect the pipes together to pass the level.<br><br>Rotate the pipes, make a path, but think logically about the connections and try to make a proper flow and solve the puzzle. There is a 50 levels to complete, and the challenge becomes increasingly difficult as you progress. Enjoy a relaxing time connecting pipes.<br><br>In PIP 2:<br><br>- 50 levels<br>- Cool art<br>- Achievements<br>- Relax music<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.apng?t=1745451521\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.poster.avif?t=1745451521\" class=\"bb_img\" width=75 height=21 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.apng?t=1745451521\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.poster.avif?t=1745451521\" class=\"bb_img\" width=75 height=21 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.apng?t=1745451521\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.poster.avif?t=1745451521\" class=\"bb_img\" width=75 height=21 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.apng?t=1745451521\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115470/extras/45bd19e01eaae62cbab05533de195ba2.poster.a